data.title: Boxers Gene Tunney and Jack Dempsey, 1964
data.meta_description: REMEMBER WHEN?-It wasn't until Wednesday-37 years to the day since their battle of the long count-that Gene Tunney, left, and Jack Dempsey got together again. They're dabbling in politics at the moment and will be honored at several testimonial affairs this weekend in the Riverside County area.
